Class AsteroidsGameTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.byu.cs.superasteroids.AsteroidsGame

  • public class AsteroidsGameTypes
extends java.lang.Object
    Created by Marshall Garey on 1/18/2016. This is a container for all the information about game objects that we need in order to play the game. It just contains lists of various game data.
